.value.resource_description: Congratulations! You've got a free textbook. Download this guide to learn how to use it.
The Student Answer Guide contains answers to a subset of the problems and exercises in the text.
This resource provides the answers to the Be Prepared questions that begin each section of the textbook.
This collection of worksheets uses manipulatives to help you understand the concepts behind mathematical procedures and how and why they work.
This set of 20 activities connects math-themed children’s books to topics in your textbook, giving you a simple, fun perspective on key topics and how they apply to real life situations.

Click below to download the previous version of the Prealgebra PDF. This version was used beginning in June 2017. The only difference between this version and the one available under “Get the book” in the Book Details tab is the numbering of Tables. The version under “Get this book” corrects an issue with table numbering.
Adapted from OpenStax College Success, this guide discusses effective reading approaches, study tips, and notetaking strategies for students.
Adapted from OpenStax College Success, this guide includes information about estimating time on tasks, avoiding procrastination, and using strategies to stick to your priorities.
